<item>
            <title>[HBASE-4787] Make corePool as a configurable parameter in HTable</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4787</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Make the corePool a configurable parameter in HTable. So we can tune this parameter in the config file.  While at it, change the core pool name so we can distinguish it from other AppServer pools.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12531405">HBASE-4787</key>
